data.description: This 4 bed, 1.5 story Lee's Summit home features main floor Owner's Suite, formal dining/ office and open kitchen & living room layout with wonderful built ins.Convenient  Utility Room just off the kitchen! 2nd level offers 3 additional large bedrooms all with walk in closets & a full bath. Relax in your screened-in, privacy enhanced, covered back deck overlooking the irrigated lawn. Newer stainless steel appliances, Newer main level paint, Updated AC/furnace, newer roof. The full, unfinished basement is ready for storage or finishing. Subdivision pool. Close to amenities! This is truly an ideal Lee's Summit 1.5 Story opportunity!
